Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:13.39,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,今まさに宇宙はspace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.60,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂一つのsweet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.97,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,甘い甘いチューtaste
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:23.30,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂一つのsweet
